  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6718523">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6718523/" class="title-link">什么是西方</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6718523"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/58774025/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/58774025/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-27"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-27 14:46:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6718523_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         尼摩的这本《什么是西方》真是大胆之作。读完全书，收获还是非常非常多的。但是个人觉得本书在方法论问题上存在硬伤，但与此同时，也有许多的闪光之笔。鉴于方法论问题具有优先性，因此先兵后礼，首先分析本书的方法论问题，然后再指出本书的闪光之处。  【方法论问题】...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6718523/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6718523_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6718523_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4904879">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4904879/" class="title-link">基督的救赎</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4904879"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/dodo22mi/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1344792-28.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dodo22mi/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">月球背面</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-12"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-12 21:19:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4904879_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         读此书后最大的收获是认识到了基督教对于西方精神最终形成并有别于其他文化所起到的巨大而又独特的作用。众所周知，希腊的民主是当代民主政治的奠基石，它否定了君主神权和专制统治，摒除了对极权崇拜的迷信并肯定了多元化言论相对于单一言论的优越性。而罗马法对于私有...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4904879/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4904879_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4904879_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





